Some tips about how to write an essay.

Dataset description(eg. Crowdcounting dataset):
1. Characteristics (specific task, source)
  The dataset was first created/collected for a task from a video camera ...
2. Scalibility
  The dataset consists of 2000 frames of size H x W ...
  The dataest contains a total of 49,885 pedestrain instances and it is split into training and test set.
3. Annotations
  A region-pf-interest is also provided to ignore unnecessary moving objects such as trees.
4. Drawbacks
  This dataset has relatively low density crowd with an average of around 15 people in a frame.
